release_note: Vocre has been updated for iOS 14. Here are some of the updates: Added 8 new languages: Bangla Gujarati Khmer Kurdish Nepali Punjabi Tamil Telugu iOS 14 home screen widget Dark Mode Offline voice translation Subscription to remove ads and give all languages and offline mode Squashed several annoying bugs If you love Vocre please write a review on the app store. It really helps. Thank you!

Vocre now supports 59 languages from Catalan to Swahili and many in between . Some languages have more features than others please check the description and tell us if we should support another language that isn t listed. Enjoy and don t hesitate to leave us a review in the app store. Changes: Fix Cantonese language bug Faster translations Less ads

Changes: Fixed a crash issue caused by playing Apple Music when launching Vocre Improve translation speed and accuracy Updated language libraries based on user feedback Increased speed of translation reduced number of errors! Fixed a major bug that was causing translation errors for many users! If you like Vocre would you mind taking a moment to write a nice review on the App Store We d greatly appreciate it. Just tap the heart button inside the app. Thanks for using Vocre! If you re have any questions or concerns please contact our support team at support vocre.com

Vocre Translate now plays nice with iPhone 5 iOS6 Disabled screen rotation in Table Top mode it s now easier to reference a translation without the screen auto rotating. Several super awesome bug fixes. Vocre Translate is no longer free. GASP! Don t worry it s still free for YOU since you ve already downloaded it... and you re special. By making Vocre a paid app we can continue to improve the app you know and love. Hand held mode has been temporarily disabled app update coming soon!
iPad3 New iPad Retina Support Simplified starting a conversation Super important usability bug and organizational fixes New info screen: more info tutorial how to videos and more good stuff
Fixed critical speech recognition issue Added Brazilian Portuguese Set it FREE!!

New in Vocre 1.1 A simplified rotation based Hand Held mode w available step by step tutorial. iPhone iPod Touch Only A NEW Table Top conversation mode Portrait Landscape 13 New Languages!
